{"tid":963062,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友自從轉咗新公司之後好多應酬","createTime":"2018-12-31T10:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T14:59:40.000Z","uid":130725,"like":44,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b53645ec0c7b36450387fbfd9b2f49ec436e51","tid":963062,"uid":130725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"班同事好中意飲酒，每逢節日都會圍埋一齊圍喂喂飲酒，唔係話唔好嘅，男人返工有好嘅人際關係先會做嘢方便，但自己奈何唔太中意佢成日飲酒。上次聖誕個排飲到醉曬覆都冇覆過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日31號，公司早放3點，佢約好咗我收工之後做完gym就去食下晚飯影相，點知啲同事由下午一點食lunch開始飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紅酒白酒啤酒乜都有，已經暗示咗佢聽想佢快啲返，結果飲到以家影到冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉我以家自己一個on99係佢屋企等佢覆，個心真係好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你地聽我呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365ecaeeb5902ed77849fad35c3517299453c9b5","tid":963062,"uid":62514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b0e96ddce37848fc4e9f88000a3a86a3297032","tid":963062,"uid":20066,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"人地陪緊女同事倒數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dd47a344e3d0a11d5cb66fa6f35ce6271e25e4","tid":963062,"uid":53238,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:21:51.000Z","msg":"你都識講啦<br />\n唔同 d 女同事混熟做野邊會方便"},{"pid":"5d03e6647848c72541057b2baa37512f1f07a6ee","tid":963062,"uid":130725,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"嬲到喊，以家話醉左cancel晚飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d393e6927d8158ef19ccdfd15479025da4f41118","ti